snippet.title: Jewels of Babylon walkthrough (C64 - Interceptor Software)
snippet.description:
Jewels of Babylon (https://www.mobygames.com/game/c64/jewels-of-babylon) was a graphics adventure game published by Interceptor Software in 1985 for the Commodore 64.

Hope you enjoy the walkthrough!

The long play is done by Smartadventurer, a program that I wrote to automate the playing for vintage Apple ][ games. You can follow the project here: https://vinniethelung.wordpress.com/tag/smartadventurer/

Credits:
Cover art - www.mobygames.com
Walkthrough - www.
